data.author: Enrique Fernandez
data.message:
Merge branch 'support_tilted_xtion' into 'master'

Support Tilted Xtion

Add pid gains for a revolute joint defining the pose of a Xtion camera on top of the mobile base.

A revolute joint with 0 limits needs to be defined for the Xtion pose wrt /base_link in order to get the point cloud properly generated. Fake PID parameters must be defined for this revolute joint.

data.author: Jordi Pages
data.message:
Add pids for a xtion revolute joint

A revolute joint with 0 limits needs to be defined for the Xtion pose wrt /base_link in order to get the point cloud properly generated in simulation. Using fixed joints is not supported by Gazebo and this is the typical workaround, i.e. defining a revolute joint with 0 limits and
fake PID parameters.
